---
---
<section class="dark-block" id="story">
  <div class="split">
    <div class="split-art" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div>
      <div class="section-eyebrow">002 · The story</div>
      <h3>Built by creators who'd <em>done it the hard way.</em></h3>
      <p>
        Most creator income is hiding in plain sight — buried under thousands of campaigns,
        dozens of dashboards, and reports that arrive two days late.
      </p>
      <p>
        We built Creator Coders for ourselves first, after years of doing the work by hand.
        Now it runs in the background, and we'd rather not go back.
      </p>
      <p class="cite">— Made by creator-coders, for creators.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dark-block { background: var(--espresso); color: var(--cream); }
  .split {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 120px 32px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px; align-items: center;
  }
  .split-art {
    background: linear-gradient(155deg, var(--pink) 0%, var(--peach) 55%, var(--gold) 100%);
    aspect-ratio: 4/5; border-radius: 8px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .split-art::before {
    content: '< / >';
    position: absolute; bottom: 32px; left: 32px;
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-style: italic; font-size: 72px;
    color: rgba(26,20,16,0.85);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1;
  }
  .split-art::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 32px; right: 32px;
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%; background: var(--espresso);
  }
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--peach); margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  h3 {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  h3 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--peach); }
  p {
    font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--warm-on-dark); margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  p.cite {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-style: italic; font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted-on-dark);
    margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(251,247,243,0.12);
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .split { padding: 80px 24px; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .split-art { max-width: 360px; }
  }
</style>
